# List of notable files and directories

**Prisma Schema:** `prisma/schema.prisma`

**ShadCN Components:** `src/components/shadcn`
- All shadcn components should be placed in this directory
- Components include: button, dialog, input, label, sidebar, toast, etc.
- Each component has its own file (e.g., `button.tsx`, `dialog.tsx`)
- Hooks and utilities for components are also placed here (e.g., `use-toast.ts`)